abstract: Strong Labor Dept jobs report shakes up stock market as investors predict that Federal Reserve will likely stop keeping interest rates close to zero.
lead_paragraph: As employment numbers come in line with Fed targets, investors worry that the days of near-zero interest will come to an end sooner than expected.

headline.main: Market Retreats as Strong Jobs Report Prompts Fears of Fed Action
headline.print_headline: Market Retreats as Strong Jobs Report Prompts Fears of Fed Action
